snippet.title: FINAL FANTASY XIV Patch 4.3 - Under the Moonlight
snippet.description:
Lord Hien’s negotations with the imperial envoy Asahi are proceeding apace, and their forthcoming prisoner exchange promises a burgeoning peace between Doma and the Empire. Yet now is not the time for repose─adventure beckons! Brave the dangers of the Valnard Sea in a parlous quest to find Ivalice, or traverse the uncharted wilds of Eureka and discover what became of the isle of Val.

Great trials and still greater rewards await those who would stand against the coming peril. With all this and more fast approaching, we offer you a sneak peek with the Patch 4.3 — Under the Moonlight trailer!

Visit the 4.3 special site: https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/patch/4_3

#FFXIV #MMO #Stormblood
